{
  "_comment": "Tier-1 mcp_tool source presets for container-manager-mcp (AU-KG.ingest.mcp-tool-connector). Declarative sync of the Docker/Podman/Kubernetes inventory into the KG via the container-manager-mcp MCP server. Docker/Podman presets: containers/images. Kubernetes presets: k8s-pods (cm_k8s_workloads/list_pods), k8s-deployments (cm_k8s_workloads/list_services, Deployment-shaped), k8s-namespaces (cm_k8s_config/list_namespaces), k8s-services (cm_k8s_networking/list_k8s_services). For full typed-node ingestion (containers/images/volumes/networks/services/nodes + pods/deployments/namespaces/k8s_services + :usesImage/:runsOn/:runsInNamespace links) call the cm_ingest_inventory tool instead — the full-fidelity path. Contributed presets win over the central MCP_TOOL_PRESETS.",
